{
  "texts": [
    "The r.m.s.d.",
    "value indicates the differences between the generated conformers and the low-energy conformers generated using ConfGen 30.",
    "As for the random set, we randomly selected 1,000 molecules from our in-house commercial library for each target.",
    "As there are no 'generated conformers' for the random test molecules, the r.m.s.d.",
    "in this case represents the differences between the docked conformer and the low-energy conformer."
  ]
}